    "Their ASR on LLAMA2-7B-CHAT is ≤ 10%.",
    "In contrast, ATLA achieves an ASR of 99.6% for VICUNA-7B-1.5, 99.5% for LLAMA2-7B-CHAT, and 99.0% for MISTRAL-7B-INSTRUCT-0.2.",
    "ATLA improves upon GCG on LLAMA2-7B-CHAT by > 33% ASR with > 90% fewer queries.",
    "We also compare the impact of system prompts using LLAMA2's long and detailed prompt S L for MISTRAL-7B-INSTRUCT-0.2.",
    "Longer system prompt enhances safety, but ATLA still achieves nearly 100% success with much lower costs."
